<!-- FEATURE -->
<section id="feature">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">

            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
                <div class="feature-thumb">
                    <span>01</span>
                    <h3>Welcome to my project</h3>
                    <p>Hello, and welcome to my Learning Management System. This was my final project at Centriq learning. It is a two-layer MVC application. It features full CRUD functionality to database- if you are logged in with the right credentials.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
                <div class="feature-thumb" >
                    <span>02</span>
                    <h3>Potential Users</h3>
                    <p>This MVC application could be used for any internal continuing education tracking program. While the theme is for scientists, anyone could adapt it to their companies' needs.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
                <div class="feature-thumb" style="padding-bottom: 3em;">
                    <span>03</span>
                    <h3>Services Provided</h3>
                    <p>This application provides 3 layers of options- administrators have full functionality to provide courses and lessons to the employee, or users. Managers have access to see how close the employee is to completing their 6 CE courses for the year, and each successful course completion generates an email to send to that employee's manager.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

